      "Focused helpers like Snippet Generator and Price Checker streamline everyday decisions.",
  },
];
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <section class="bg-slate-950 py-10 text-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-white/70">Features</p>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-black tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">
          Everything inside the Ansiversa ecosystem
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base text-white/70">
          Discover the polished capabilities powering our AI-driven mini-apps‚Äîfrom intuitive onboarding to premium content drops.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm font-semibold">
          <a href="/pricing" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-slate-950 shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/30 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-100">
            Compare plans
          </a>
          <a href="/#mini-apps" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/30 px-6 py-3 text-white/80 transition hover:border-white/60 hover:text-white">
            Browse mini-apps
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white py-16 text-slate-900">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-indigo-500">Platform Capabilities</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
